# Git Configuration Setup

## Overview
This project uses a conditional Git configuration setup that changes user identity based on the repository location.

## Configuration Files
- `~/.gitconfig`: Main Git configuration file with default settings
- `~/.gitconfig-deblock`: Conditional configuration for deblock-hq repositories
- `~/.gitconfig.backup`: Backup of the original configuration

## Configuration Details

### Default Configuration
The default configuration uses:
- Email: bufka@dupa.pl
- Name: Marcin Kubica
- GPG signing enabled
- Custom hooks path
- Auto setup remote for push
- Fast-forward only for pull

### Deblock-specific Configuration
